Ext.data.JsonP['Studio_4.9.0.GA_Release_Note']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Studio 4.9.0.GA - 2 June 2017</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-49162216\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Studio 4.9.0.GA - 2 June 2017</h1>\n    <p>Studio 4.9.0.GA is a minor release that includes new features, improvements and bug fixes.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-49162216_Studio4.9.0.GAReleaseNote-Newfeatures\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>New features</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/GB-521\" target=\"_blank\">GB-521</a> - App Designer for Windows Phone apps    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Added support to use App Designer for Windows Phones    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-7138\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-7138</a> - AppceleratorStudio: Unable to configure which IP should the LiveView use    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Added configurability for LiveView to be set with select IP. Please review <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/LiveView\">LiveView</a> for details.    </p>\n</li></ul></li></ul>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-49162216_Studio4.9.0.GAReleaseNote-Improvements\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Improvements</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/GB-501\" target=\"_blank\">GB-501</a> - Add search/filter bar in the Properties view    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Added a search/filter field in the Properties view    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/GB-535\" target=\"_blank\">GB-535</a> - Default size of the mobile screen to fit into a page    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Configured default zoom percentages based on the mobile screen fit into the designer page    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Added default zoom percentages for mobile web    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Changed the text from &quot;1080x1920 iPhone 6+&quot; to 1080x1920 iPhone 6 Plus&quot;    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Changed &quot;Snap To&quot; combo to uneditable    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/GB-539\" target=\"_blank\">GB-539</a> - Properties - App Designer: Enable Delete with Keyboard Delete on ColorCellEditors    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Added support to delete the assigned color for ColorCell type values    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/GB-540\" target=\"_blank\">GB-540</a> - Allow deselect of elements in App Designer    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Added support to deselect element from the Cursor key icon from the editor toolbar or by tapping the ESC key    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-7979\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-7979</a> - Liveview for the Windows Platform    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Implemented LiveView for the Windows    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8538\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8538</a> - Publishing: Block field input until &apos;Use Existing&apos; is selected by the user on Windows Phone packaging    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Locked input fields for certificate location and password unless the user selects the <tt class=\" \">Use Existing</tt> option    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8557\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8557</a> - limit the size of a symbol file uploaded to crashserver to 250Mb    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Set limit of 250MB of symbol file uploads to crashserver    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8563\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8563</a> - Studio startup performance improvement    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Improved Studio startup performance    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8570\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8570</a> - Remove call to provisioner.py    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Deprecated Studio&apos;s use of <tt class=\" \">provisioner.py</tt> script    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8579\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8579</a> - Android: Update link to Android tools    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Revised Studio&apos;s update link for Android tooling    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8598\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8598</a> - Arrow: Handle error from Arrow deployment better    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Improved error handling when <tt class=\" \">appc publish</tt> returns an error when an app cannot be started    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8605\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8605</a> - Studio must no longer rely on wait_for_device.py    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Deprecated <tt class=\" \">wait_for_device.py</tt>    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8668\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8668</a> - Studio should not use removed options for build commands    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Deprecated <tt class=\" \">sim-type</tt> and <tt class=\" \">sim-version</tt> from Studio    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8685\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8685</a> - Upgrade Appcelerator Studio JDK version to 1.8    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Upgrade Studio JDK version to JDK 1.8    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8713\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8713</a> - Provide example AppID format in the new project creation wizard    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Improved the New Project Creation wizard to include a sample AppID in the app ID form    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>For example: <tt class=\" \">com.companyname.appname</tt>    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8714\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8714</a> - Avoid showing error reporting message sent confirmation pop-up dialog    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Removed redundant error reporting server confirmation message after the error has been sent to the server    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8718\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8718</a> - Send error reports in the silent mode by default    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Changed the default error reporting send action from &quot;Ask before sending&quot; to &quot;Always send silently&quot;    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8729\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8729</a> - Add support for enterprise ad hoc provisioning profiles    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Added support for enterprise ad hoc provisioning profiles    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8747\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8747</a> - Update node installer links to Node.js v6.10.3(Latest LTS)    <span style=\"color: #ffcc00;\">\n<br>    </br></span>\n    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-49162216_Studio4.9.0.GAReleaseNote-FixedIssues\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Fixed Issues</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-7569\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-7569</a> - The studio login dialog after entering wrong credentials does not close on cancel    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-7826\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-7826</a> - Error reporting: NPE in Control.internal_new_GC    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-7872\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-7872</a> - Studio does not find 5.1.0.GA    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-7965\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-7965</a> - Windows Login: Bad layout on Windows (using Retina screen)    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-7984\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-7984</a> - Studio: UI element draw issue and frequent crash when closing a separate editor window    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8502\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8502</a> - Windows: Local Machine missing from run-list    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8527\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8527</a> - Norton Security deems Appc Studio unsafe, and Symantec Endpoint Protection think the install is untrustworthy    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8551\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8551</a> - Windows: Studio requires Windows SDK path to be set for project creation    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8556\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8556</a> - Remove Windows SDK path configuration from the Platform configuration dialog    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8561\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8561</a> - Studio dashboard opening page blocks the user doing other activities    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8566\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8566</a> - During the studio launch &quot;Validating Status&quot; is taking long time    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8571\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8571</a> - tiapp.xml editor schema doesn&apos;t allow comma-separated deploy types on modules    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8575\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8575</a> - LiveView: vEthernet network connection is selected when building on a Windows system    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8584\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8584</a> - Error reporting: Unknown SDK windows    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8588\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8588</a> - Windows: &apos;Mobile App Project&apos; dropdown on module packaging is blank    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8596\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8596</a> - CLI:Platform specific folders are not created under resources when additional deployment targets are selected from tiapp.xml    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8600\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8600</a> - Studio console log does not show debug logs while building/packaging android module.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8603\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8603</a> - Alloy: Unable to create an alloy component when right clicking on file    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8638\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8638</a> - Visual elements not lining up correctly    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8656\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8656</a> - Studio freezes momentarily when opening or closing files    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8662\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8662</a> - Hide Windows Preference page in Mac OS    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8665\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8665</a> - Disclaimer Text on Login Screen for 13&quot; Mac running Windows    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8675\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8675</a> - Studio: Error is produced when trying to configure with no options selected    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8676\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8676</a> - Studio: &quot;No write Permissions&quot; warning in Platform configuration for iOS    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8684\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8684</a> - Mac Installer: Problems with installing JDK    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8688\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8688</a> - Windows Platform Configuration is shown on Mac    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8696\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8696</a> - Liveview: Unable to find Hyperloop reference on iOS devices    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8698\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8698</a> - Windows Platform available as deployment target for a project on Mac OS    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8701\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8701</a> - Link to installing JDT Tools goes to wrong page    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8703\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8703</a> - Error reporting: NPE after launching the Studio    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8705\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8705</a> - Error reporting: Inspect IdeLog.logError() references in the studio    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8707\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8707</a> - Error reporting: Could not find default Android SDK error during App preview    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8710\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8710</a> - Error reporting: Null or Empty type name attempting to be recorded for a return type    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8711\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8711</a> - Error reporting: No provider registered for Ti SDK 4.1 Example    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8720\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8720</a> - Cannot access API Docs when running Arrow on Local Server    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8721\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8721</a> - Exception:java.lang.Error: Error: could not match input    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8724\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8724</a> - Updating Android NDK path does not update configuration file in Windows    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8727\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8727</a> - NPE during sign out from studio    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8740\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8740</a> - &quot;Manage AVDs&quot; button in Android preference not working with new Android-Tools release    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8741\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8741</a> - Studio dashboard shows &quot;Server unavailable&quot; page with the CLI 6.2.0-master.62    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8753\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8753</a> - Exception when trying to open &quot;About Appcelerator Studio&quot;    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8754\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8754</a> - Studio continuously prompts user to install Java Development Kit 1.8.0_121 if they don&apos;t already have Java 1.8 installed    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8760\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8760</a> - Android: Debugging for android device throws &quot;java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: org/chromium/sdk/JavascriptVmFactory&quot;    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-8772\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-8772</a> - Hyperloop: Errors when running project with liveview and hyperloop enabled    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-49162216_Studio4.9.0.GAReleaseNote-Knownissues\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Known issues</span></h2>\n    <p><strong class=\" \">    <span style=\"color: #16233a;\">\nManaging Android AVDs using Axway Appcelerator Studio 4.9.0.    </span>\n</strong><br>    <span style=\"color: #16233a;\">\nWith Android SDK Tools 25.3.0 (March, 2017) and higher, there is a change in how we manage Android AVD creation in Studio. Google has deprecated the &#x201C;android&#x201D; command which was used to launch Android AVD Manager UI and this is not possible now with Android SDK Tools 25.3.0 and higher.    </span>\n    </br></p>\n    <p>    <span style=\"color: #16233a;\">\n     </span>\n    <span style=\"color: #16233a;\">\nTo address this, Studio 4.9.0 has implemented a new UI to allow basic Android AVD creation by capturing the AVD name, device, and system image.     </span>\n    </p>\n    <p>    <span style=\"color: #16233a;\">\n     </span>\n    <span style=\"color: #16233a;\">\nHowever, to customize the AVD creation, users can use a new program called     </span>\n    <span style=\"color: #16233a;\">\n<strong class=\" \">avdmanager</strong> in the<strong class=\" \"> tools/bin</strong> folder of your Android SDK from the command line tools.    </span>\n    </p>\n    <p>    </p>\n    <p><strong class=\" \">    <span style=\"color: #16233a;\">\nNote:     </span>\n</strong>    <span style=\"color: #16233a;\">\nIt&#x2019;s recommended to use Android Tools 25.2.5 and lower or 25.3.2 and higher.    </span>\n    </p>\n    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=49162216\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Studio 4.9.0.GA Release Note"});